org.deeplearning4j.ui.flow.beans

Class ModelInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.ui.flow.beans.ModelInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ModelInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This bean works as holder for unbounded list of layers. Each layer has it's own place in model's virtual coordinate space. For now, coordinate space is limited to 2 dimensions
